<h1>Existing User</h1>
<p>A user with the name <strong><%= @user.name %></strong> already exists.</p>
<br>
<% if @user.image.present? %>
	<%= image_tag @user.image.g3.url, :class => 'g3 square' %>
	<br>
<% end %>
<p class="note">The user joined <%= time_ago_in_words @user.created_at %> _password.</p>
<br>

<h4>That's me!</h4>
<p>
	Please <%= link_to 'login', login_path %> using one of your verified login methods.
	If you wish to add <%= @provider %> login, you can do so after logging in by going to the Account > Login Settings page.
</p>
<br>
<h4>Must be someone else...</h4>
<p>
	Try <%= link_to 'signing up', signup_path %> using another username, or <%= link_to 'logging in', login_path %> using one of your already verified login methods.
</p>